{"tid":1544712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔傻撚哂？奶共宇宙gem著件黑print tee就打哂飛機？","createTime":"2019-09-05T15:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T17:44:18.000Z","uid":85390,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2024cbbcb5c759b7b3f8105796528e4368696b93","tid":1544712,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:58:11.000Z","msg":"呢隻奶共狗由5-6件前已經現哂形，你班友因爲佢著件黑print tee就覺得佢係撐呢邊？ 屌你老味無撚腦，佢啲黑歷史講到口水都乾：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//她除了撰文講述自己的音樂理想之外，還撐特首，指梁振英必然承受極大壓力。她在文中提到有時打開報紙，見到有人很激烈地反對某些事，或者從早到晚叫特首下台，她會覺得：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嘩！使唔使呀？</span></span></strong></span>」，更認為不覺得一個特首、或者一個政府可以怎樣幫助市民。文章隨即引起迴響，有人指她不分青紅皂白支持梁振英的理由牽強，而親共組織則支持其言論。文中的一些句子更演變成萬能key以諷刺她。<br />\n<br />\n鄧紫棋2014年事件<br />\n2014年鄧紫棋參加大陸選秀節目《我是歌手2》爆紅，成為「國際G.E.M.」、「宇宙G.E.M.」。其發展重心主要放在大陸，香港網民認為她忘本、飲水不思源，觀感更惡化。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>年底雨傘革命她採取曖昧的取態</strong></span></span>，佔領區出現「共狗棋」的標語。<br />\n參加大陸歌唱比賽爆紅<br />\n<br />\n2014年10月下旬，鄧紫棋往荷蘭接受上太空前的訓練，並在facebook上載有關照片。當中一張照片他<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">身穿太空裝，但上面有中國國旗</span></strong></span>，引起爭議，結果令到兩批網民發生大罵戰。[19]自此鄧紫棋又多了一個名號：「太空G.E.M.」<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多 自己search或者睇大典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/鄧紫棋\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%E9%84%A7%E7%B4%AB%E6%A3%8B&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=7c7200b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/鄧紫棋</a>"},{"pid":"fde13baf7cee1b13885ff804ad2785bbfb64db8e","tid":1544712,"uid":119173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64061078c6998ccdd955185c1393d60e80e8b71e","tid":1544712,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fde13baf7cee1b13885ff804ad2785bbfb64db8e","tid":1544712,"uid":119173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9249ea3de29a86e8a21add36d9a3587609cf8d","tid":1544712,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25baa2df5d2fa96cbe5aca7375e6db9ed7003de2","tid":1544712,"uid":104935,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"有邊個年少未試過無知<br />\n好多5年前政治冷感嘅大人都今次守護香港啦<br />\n你同個5個前仲係靚妹嘅人清算舊帳？<br />\n佢一直唔護旗，黑衫黑罩我覺得要connect啦"},{"pid":"bde93046b3234fb6f89609312f44541e0f390941","tid":1544712,"uid":104935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25baa2df5d2fa96cbe5aca7375e6db9ed7003de2","tid":1544712,"uid":104935,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"有邊個年少未試過無知<br />\n好多5年前政治冷感嘅大人都今次守護香港啦<br />\n你同個5個前仲係靚妹嘅人清算舊帳？<br />\n佢一直唔護旗，黑衫黑罩我覺得要connect啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:44:18.000Z","msg":"Btw係兩次黑衫黑罩了"}]}